{"tid":714201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Official】連登時事台國際飲食排名","createTime":"2018-06-23T13:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T17:56:43.000Z","uid":131691,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c7b5b023a0e914d0b35a6f0c7623e768c3f356","tid":714201,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"經過念力諮詢各位時事台手足之後，我呢位得閒過頭嘅廢青終於establish咗連登時事台嘅official各國料理飲食排名。圖文並茂，請過目。如有錯漏請補充。<br />\n<br />\n你現在聚腳在  時事台內。<br />\n<br />\n1. 無敵級：香港料理，西多士<br />\nInvincible tier: Hong Kong cuisine, French toast<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205042_b68a386f2d97aa437c03cfab701cc64e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205042_b68a386f2d97aa437c03cfab701cc64e.jpg&h=e34dff56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 神級：法國料理，紅酒炆雞<br />\nGod tier: French cuisine, Coq au vin<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205221_d32c2c36de81a7d7c5486643a9b8b0e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205221_d32c2c36de81a7d7c5486643a9b8b0e9.jpg&h=c7f75fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 事頭婆級：英國料理，牛肉牛腰批<br />\nRule Britannia tier: British cuisine, Steak and kidney suet pudding<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205612_1c085d76c858931fe64848f9244a7cf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205612_1c085d76c858931fe64848f9244a7cf2.jpg&h=2258ade7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 二次元級：日本料理，傳統日式早餐<br />\n2D tier: Japanese cuisine, traditional Japanese breakfast<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205747_86ecc16ada130ff250e5b2330cdb6172.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205747_86ecc16ada130ff250e5b2330cdb6172.jpg&h=3955df04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 送啤酒級：德國料理，德國香腸<br />\nBier tier: German cuisine, Wurst platter<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205627_1878a9d8dd8d63cbcfdfd02e1c647cfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205627_1878a9d8dd8d63cbcfdfd02e1c647cfb.jpg&h=40f7566e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 仙樂飄飄處處聞級：奧地利料理，奧地利豬扒<br />\nThe hills are alive tier: Austrian cuisine, Wienerschnitzel<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205807_816748d3e6f600d1c2fca6002ded42f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205807_816748d3e6f600d1c2fca6002ded42f2.jpg&h=03221807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 南歐熱情級：西班牙料理，西班牙飯<br />\nMoorish tier: Spanish cuisine, Paella<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/205902_3ca9ae605677fcd4eac7713780d7833c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F205902_3ca9ae605677fcd4eac7713780d7833c.jpg&h=5914f82f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 窮撚急就章級：意大利料理，妓女意粉<br />\nThrow everything in tier: Italian cuisine, Spaghetti Puttanesca<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/210110_f173efe18c64f3b36bdfb2ac32f887c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F210110_f173efe18c64f3b36bdfb2ac32f887c7.jpg&h=f7c32405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 食完肚屙級：印度料理，羊肉咖喱<br />\nDiarrhoea tier: Indian cuisine, Rogan josh<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/210207_4971f6f8b41a1771aee17a27356dbaf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F210207_4971f6f8b41a1771aee17a27356dbaf0.jpg&h=144655c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10. 被茶餐廳級：俄羅斯料理，羅宋湯<br />\nCyka blyat tier: Russian cuisine, Borscht<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/210348_0f4d4d524759ed20ccd5ce21a83261e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F210348_0f4d4d524759ed20ccd5ce21a83261e2.jpg&h=117aba54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超過9000. 昆蟲級：地獄鬼國料理，？？？<br />\nSubhuman tier: Modern Chinese cuisine<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/212026_fec1ccd63f0bf7454ffa446b0de66f71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F212026_fec1ccd63f0bf7454ffa446b0de66f71.jpg&h=5d88e5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/212327_43654ec3e9de6acc8f990a467a4c848b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F212327_43654ec3e9de6acc8f990a467a4c848b.jpeg&h=f00244d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/212335_26780cfb4ffe4c889f29992d2cbafd28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F212335_26780cfb4ffe4c889f29992d2cbafd28.jpg&h=e919b077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/211950_10269e3b8da0d7fad9553c90448cd078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F211950_10269e3b8da0d7fad9553c90448cd078.jpg&h=9258e687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/211108_8dd76106cd6e8af5a998b61a831ba0f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F211108_8dd76106cd6e8af5a9